149
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:11,291
It's a respectable...
That's where I met Virginia.

150
00:11:11,416 --> 00:11:15,713
You tell Marty to go to the Stardust
Ballroom. It's loaded with tomatoes.

151
00:11:16,046 --> 00:11:20,010
"The Stardust Ballroom.
